-- FlyDubai's Chief Financial Officer Mills Hired to Head India's SpiceJet
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-07-08T08:02:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/flydubai-s-chief-financial-officer-mills-hired-to-head-india-s-spicejet.html

          
          
             FlyDubai Chief Financial Officer  Neil Mills  is leaving the company after a year in the role and will
join India’s SpiceJet Ltd. as chief executive officer.  
 “This is a terrific opportunity for Neil and we wish him
all the best in his future role,”  Ghaith Al Ghaith , FlyDubai’s
chief executive officer said in an e-mailed statement today.  
